個可能：1.中國吞併台灣 2.台灣吞併中國<br />\n係人都會覺得1機會較大，但世事「欲盡不盡不可說」<br />\n共慘黨2020年會成大錯，而中華民國可能會亡於美國(雕)手上，難保其實係共慘黨出事後美國介入，協助台灣統一中國！！！！！！！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"我估係正式宣布中華民國收皮，正名台灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"始艱危  終克定<br />\n可指2024台灣最終奪回中國<br />\n亦符合其中一象指中華民國只有10位總統"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"好快中華民國就正名做台灣，咁中華民國呢個名就係歷史"},{"pid":"41bea5658bdd625f0b2f0e2ed79e3ff01184531e","tid":1841901,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"25年咩事都冇發生就移民了"},{"pid":"38291c99dcb14dba081eef581769994619ea3e23","tid":1841901,"uid":181655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62c2b52b6149d5085ddf15b7afd609f232efc5ec","tid":1841901,"uid":236108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:56:04.000Z","msg":"咁撚多預言 實有個中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"個個預言都指呢個時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9da656447fb7848f90bc61f4a3ef92cd9521a9","tid":1841901,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"我想知&ldquo;青青草&rdquo;，呢個五十年中一將臣，會係邊個"},{"pid":"accecff7395250e9bc5caae5d4cdf075ff74dd5c","tid":1841901,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"高汁post<br />\n<br />\n原樓主：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n芥_蘭_強<br />\n#90<br />\n3 年前<br />\n其實而家共產黨同國民黨冇咩分別，都係搞一黨專政<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係共產黨拎番民國法統，改番叫中華民國，台灣就變自治，同香港一樣?<br />\n大膽猜測，由於共慘黨2020會成大錯，中國2024年前會衰到貼地(2024後否極泰來)<br />\n所以可能係指共慘黨2020年出大錯後唔能掂，要勁縮返去秦州(陝西)<br />\n中國會分成九個部分(包含台灣)，2023-2024之間台灣會重返中國，或者係以邦聯、聯邦之類既形式結合！<br />\n<br />\n而2024年後中國會出聖人，哩個人可能就係邦聯制既第一任總統，所以先有「四夷重譯稱天子」<br />\n就好似古代封建時代，各地諸侯封王，但居中有一個大家認頭既人做天子！"},{"pid":"e689d5086c4383b3a3dfd6d5d78137f32691ea95","tid":1841901,"uid":120070,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"睇到中段 有條友同原樓主 芥蘭強 嘈交笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個位樓主好慘 講中好多 但個時keep住比人笑鳩<br />\n有先見行得前既人 真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92826822b49701a12da82bb1852649e42c14958","tid":1841901,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4c0ced58c544d42c8031ea3dcde6cc895474023a","tid":1841901,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"樓主即將崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4130f030050de68253998facfbd0dd9dc668210b","tid":1841901,"uid":274432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"千萬唔好有事呀， 出左事邊個鎖住班生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb6cede4df93f462fd3305f085d313dc13d9ec0","tid":1841901,"uid":266176,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"講開又講<br />\n有無人記得年頭車公求簽<br />\n好多人剩係掛住睇香港支簽 畫餅不充飢<br />\n唔知原來有支簽求比沙田<br />\n心中日復自思量，時運未通怎主張；進退難為無定處，恐防患禍與災殃<br />\n解曰：出入謹慎，凡事小心<br />\n<br />\n如果你張支簽文GOOGLE下你就會發現有網站解車公簽<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mstn.org/chace/win/win_82.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mstn.org%2Fchace%2Fwin%2Fwin_82.htm&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=a0c4b10f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mstn.org/chace/win/win_82.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【北海觀音明善堂白話簡釋】<br />\n心中之事每日翻來覆去的思量，<br />\n進退難為無法決定，<br />\n時運未通問神也無解？<br />\n恐怕要先防患橫禍與災殃。<br />\n【求得此籤 】<br />\n有<span style=\"color: red;\">進退失據</span>的意思<br />\n運逢<span style=\"color: red;\">天狗</span>擋路<br />\n時運衰事連連 , <span style=\"color: red;\">多作多錯</span> ,<br />\n以致信心頓失而進退失據<br />\n切勿胡思亂想,舉棋不定<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">凡事暫緩</span> ,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">速速解送天狗 消解災難</span><br />\n急求神明改運解厄<br />\n最利偏財橫財,正財有利.<br />\n 【斷曰】<br />\n時運未通．進退失據．胡思亂想．祈福消災．<br />\n<br />\n天狗=POPO 凡事暫緩=ON9條例<br />\n其實一開始車公已經點哂條明路 點知政府可以全部炒哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw仲有聽日就係 我想睇下今年求支咩簽返黎<br />\n夠膽係車公地頭放催淚彈佢實會保佑你個on9政府啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a8556f8a91e7bc227bb1edc8320a4873bbbd6c","tid":1841901,"uid":19929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e689d5086c4383b3a3dfd6d5d78137f32691ea95","tid":1841901,"uid":120070,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"睇到中段 有條友同原樓主 芥蘭強 嘈交笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個位樓主好慘 講中好多 但個時keep住比人笑鳩<br />\n有先見行得前既人 真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T20:53:31.000Z","msg":"我係中國人呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f29ce78733ff26a5a5886fcf18a5f7ec8c3e24","tid":1841901,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:03:57.000Z","msg":"照咁解法中國有可能幾年內就有軍事政變，然後美國介入和緩局勢"},{"pid":"4631cc84bffc928d1e96e2c5ea979e3260691d04","tid":1841901,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c29af1c25a8ed68ef5b68e24b0e92bc626221644","tid":1841901,"uid":309553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3da5ff32bf16ee51864ae54551524accc07c21b","tid":1841901,"uid":81879,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"跟住第四十三象係重要既一象，因為推背圖再一次明確點出時間<br />\n第四十三象<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tuibeitu.net/upload/200903111729521173.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tuibeitu.net%2Fupload%2F200903111729521173.gif&h=3eb228d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讖曰：<br />\n君非君 臣非臣<br />\n始艱危 終克定<br />\n<br />\n頌曰：<br />\n黑兔走入青龍穴 欲盡不盡不可說<br />\n唯有外邊根樹上 三十年中子孫結<br />\n<br />\n先講時間問題<br />\n黑兔走入青龍穴，兔=兔年，龍=龍年，但幾時既兔年龍年？<br />\n五行之中水屬黑，癸屬水，所以黑兔=癸兔年<br />\n五行之中木屬青，甲屬木，所以青龍=甲龍年<br />\n2023=癸卯兔年，2024=甲辰龍年<br />\n哩句係極之明確指出事件會發生係2023-2024之間！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n發生咩事？就係君非君，臣非臣，始艱難，終克定<br />\n最接近既可能，係指台灣同中國問題<br />\n中華民國同中華人民共和國，究竟邊個係君邊個係臣？共慘黨最初只係國民黨入面分裂出黎<br />\n而重要既一句，唯有外邊根樹上 三十年中子孫結，2023-30年=1993年<br />\n共慘黨同台灣係1992年尾達成九二共識，+30年=2022年尾=2023<br />\n即係話，台灣同中國2023-2024年會有突發事件令兩國「子孫結」！！！<br />\n究竟係乜能野事！？<br />\n前面既推背圖講左中華民國會亡於雕，哩到似乎講台灣同中國會統一或者以非君非臣既形式結合(例如邦聯制)<br />\n有兩個可能：1.中國吞併台灣 2.台灣吞併中國<br />\n係人都會覺得1機會較大，但世事「欲盡不盡不可說」<br />\n共慘黨2020年會成大錯，而中華民國可能會亡於美國(雕)手上，難保其實係共慘黨出事後美國介入，協助台灣統一中國！！！！！！！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"我估係正式宣布中華民國收皮，正名台灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:19:10.000Z","msg":"老弟認同<br />\n<br />\n君非君 臣非臣應該指民主政體<br />\n三十年中子孫結：台灣立法院普選自1992年開始，普選總統自1996年開始，30年後，即2022-2026年之間，由子孫修成正果（子孫結）"},{"pid":"9ee86faddeca29ed81ae46fb534fff0dd45f9e3a","tid":1841901,"uid":61985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd799571a5e9416180f955888971eefa04b6957","tid":1841901,"uid":39215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:25:09.000Z","msg":"年年都咁講<br />\n下年又有同樣既post"},{"pid":"d59ab38f6512e4dcce16e9a9f35b124e8a781445","tid":1841901,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fd799571a5e9416180f955888971eefa04b6957","tid":1841901,"uid":39215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:25:09.000Z","msg":"年年都咁講<br />\n下年又有同樣既post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:29:15.000Z","msg":"雖然迷信，但我覺得君非君、臣非臣的確係民主政治簡單而直接嘅描述：領導人既非君主，亦非臣子"},{"pid":"6fbcd5d274d9f2df93291ae35736dc8c621c6d93","tid":1841901,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4130f030050de68253998facfbd0dd9dc668210b","tid":1841901,"uid":274432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"千萬唔好有事呀， 出左事邊個鎖住班生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 